snippet.title: Amber Heard *Exposed* by her Lawyer for Lying and Ruining Johnny Depp!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Gets Exposed By Her Lawyer For Lying And Ruining Johnny Depp's Career!

New conspiracies and information have come to light in the legal battle between famous actor Johnny Depp and actress Amber Heard! After their divorce, Amber came out and claimed that Johnny Depp has been mistreating her and her sister during the relationship.

Now, that Heard's lawyer has left her legal team and famous body language expert from the YouTube channel "Observe" has analyzed her body language in the 2016 deposition, tables are starting to slowly turn against her.
